data.text: They have all the material items they could possibly want. Privilege is perverted in an arrogant, selfish, entitled mind. There are so many sickos running around in the open. Culkin isn't one of them. Most likely, he's a victim of many of them.

He's not nuts, he's a product of his upbringing. How else would anyone handle the horrible things they've seen and been exposed to? Drugs? Alcohol? Being a nut? How would YOU handle it? These people doing this every single day.
